node.text:
We were fortunate to be able to spend an hour in the company of the incredibly inspiring @markprinceobe to discuss @thekpf and marking 15 years since Kiyan was tragically taken from us. 😔

We joined @easportsfifa @topps and @officialqpr in ensuring Kiyan legacy lives on. 👑

Check out @thekpf for more information and to donate Text KPF £5 (or another amount) to 70490

#KiyanPrince #KPF

node.text: As a victim of extreme cyber bullying, online abuse & trolling, I am well positioned to speak out against it. In a generation where 800 million people in the world suffer from mental health disorders, let us spread love not hate. A wise man once said, the kindest thing we can do to ourselves...is show kindness to others. 🔑💯☺️ Today is World Mental Health Day so I made this to lead by example & continue to use my voice & platform as a force for good. 🙏🏽❤️ #worldmentalhealthday #mentalhealthawareness

node.text: As a victim of extreme cyber bullying & online abuse, I am well positioned to speak out against it. In a generation where 800 million people in the world suffer from mental health disorders, let us spread love not hate. A wise man once said, the kindest thing we can do to ourselves...is show kindness to others. 🔑💯☺️ It’s the last day of mental health awareness week so I made this to lead by example & use my voice & platform as a force for good. ❤️ #mentalhealthawareness

node.text: Had to wait for this moment for a long time but this feeling never gets old, walking into a full stadium to watch Spurs with my boy after so long away. Nothing like it. Fans make football 💙

node.text: Jai Hind! Happy Independence Day to all Indian followers ☺️🇮🇳❤️ You probably think I don’t notice you but I do. Your positive energy is amazing & you are incredibly kind hearted & always so supportive. You are a special people & I appreciate you & celebrate this day with you all 🇮🇳❤️💪🏽 ps. Also Happy Independence Day for yesterday to Pakistan 🇵🇰❤️👊🏽☺️ I need to buy a Pakistan kit. Thank you all for your continued love & support. #india #happyindependenceday #pakistan #positiveenergy #thankyou #appreciationpost #appreciation #independenceday
